{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2544083, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哈哈哈这是thy概随第一堂课引的例子", "timestamp": 1632030986, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“而打开了一扇门后没有奖品的门。此时主持人问你是否更改你选择的门。”什么勾八句子，看了几遍没看懂", "timestamp": 1632031175, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544137, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": 2544102, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 主持人开了一扇门（不是你选择的门），而门后没有奖品。\n此时主持人问你是否仍然选择你最开始选择的那扇门", "timestamp": 1632031486, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "《决胜21点《》", "timestamp": 1632031685, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "文科生萌比了", "timestamp": 1632031835, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544186, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "换了有2/3概率获奖，不换1/3", "timestamp": 1632031860, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544358, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三门问题，下一个", "timestamp": 1632033743, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544365, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "猜测不换 概率从三分之一升高到了三分之二 cz文科生没学过概率论 如果有正确答案可以踢我一下", "timestamp": 1632033797, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544381, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "求解答，答案不是C？", "timestamp": 1632033987, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544387, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": 2544365, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 要换的", "timestamp": 1632034031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544390, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": 2544365, "tag": null, "text": "提供一个新视角：\n主持人既然能打开一扇没有奖品的门，意味着”主持人必须知道哪一扇门背后有奖品“，不然打开了有奖品的门就尴尬了。\n因此，主持人这个行为给选手提供了信息，使得剩下的门变得不对称了。", "timestamp": 1632034047, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544394, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": 2544387, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不好意思 要换 哈哈哈之前打错了", "timestamp": 1632034065, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544398, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": 2544390, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 数学上要换倒是不难证，主要是得让大家理解为什么换门会有影响。", "timestamp": 1632034084, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2544434, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 485841, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没学过概统。最好理解的算概率就是玫举。一共九种情况（放奖品三种乘以选门三种），第一次就选中是三种情况，不选中是六种情况。第二次换门后前三种情况反转为没选中，后六种情况反转为选中；第二次不换门前三种保持选中，后六种保持没选中。就是换2/3，不换1/3", "timestamp": 1632034554, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 485841, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "数学吧经典题目之2：\n你参加一个抽奖活动，面前有3扇门，其中一个门的门后有奖品。你随机选择了一个门，此时主持人不告诉你你选择的门后是否有奖品，而打开了一扇门后没有奖品的门。此时主持人问你是否更改你选择的门。你如何选择能让获奖概率更高？", "timestamp": 1632030868, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632034556, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"换": 142, "不换": 11, "换不换都一样": 22, "🍉": 23}, "vote_options": ["换", "不换", "换不换都一样", "🍉"]}}}